overview.en: Green orange Finance (Chinese name, green orange finance, token Name: gofi), is the world's first cross chain aggregate mortgage lending platform. Gofi can be understood as a decentralized inclusive financial aggregation platform and an open financial ecosystem.
overview.zh: Green Orange Finance（中文名，青橙金融，代币名称：GOFi），是全球首个跨链聚合抵押借贷平台。可以将GOFi理解为一个去中心化的普惠金融聚合平台，是个开放式的金融生态圈。
